			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">522.804-1</ph> Nonconstruction.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d447e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
					          <p id="d443e17" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The requirements of FAR 22.804 also apply to each contractor and subcontractor with 50 or more employees that either:</p>
					          <ol id="d447e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
							              <p id="d443e27" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Serves as a depository of Government funds; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
							              <p id="d443e36" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
