						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li " audience="GSAR">
					          <p id="d443e47" class="- topic/p " audience="GSAR">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contractors, subcontractors, and financial institutions described in <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "
                        base="YMNMQDHD"
                        href="GSAM-YMNMQDHD.dita#YMNMQDHD">522.804-1</xref>(a) must develop a written affirmative action compliance program for each of its establishments regardless of the contract or holding value, in accordance with 41 CFR 60-1.40.</p>
